main

Class IF

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.Command
      • main.IF

  •  class IF
extends Command
    IF takes a variable, a condition, and a value, if the variable has a value that relates to the given value using the given condition then execute will return the next Command in the list, otherwise it will return the next ENDIF statement

    the valid conditions are: !, >, <, and =
